ize=1> Yes and no, mostly no.<br><br>The first illusion mask in the game(guise of the deceiver, or dark elf mask) was clickable by any race/class from inventory. Many people old to the game have these. The current dropped verison is equip to use so bard/rog only.<br><br>Amulet of necropolice is useable by everyone from inventory, it turns you into a skeleton. Way back when this was a drop from cazic thule the god; when kunark came out and he was buffed the drop was moved to the named golems in fear plane.<br><br>Thats it for insta infinite click items. <br><br>Now single charge items....i can only think of one at the moment(its 4am heh). There was a earth elemental illusion potion in the old cazic thule, i would assume that drop has been moved to feerott now. Fun potion to mess with, but its only 1 charge.<br>Thats all i can think of this late. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=15198.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15198.topic&index=1><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=15198.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=15198.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15198.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive e